&quot;Heh, so sentinel is still active,&quot; Salveo said to himself as he stepped off
the shuttle.  &quot;We should start repairs on the defense systems as soon as
possible.&quot;

The rest of the Maxmials began moving supplies off the shuttle into the
base.

*Meanwhile....*

Having no further business, Lord Perseus lead the team out of the power room
and back toward the entrance; keeping an eye out for enemy movement.

*Control room*

As the systems powered on Kenzo walked down the line of CR chambers to the
occupied chamber and was started to find that it was already entering
activation mode.

&quot;Kenzo to team,&quot; he said into the radio.  &quot;Looks like we have 12 cycles
before our guest in the CR chamber awakens.&quot;


